_header: Now Our Lady Mary for the joys five
Subjects: Virgin Mary, prayers to; Virgin Mary, joys of; prayers, to Virgin Mary
_description: An orison to the Virgin Mary by the Five Joys — one stanza rhyme royal

Bod549.First Lines:
Now oure lady Marye for thy Ioyes fyvefferst for that Angell
                    Gabriel Salutacoun…
Bod549.Last Lines:
…Wyth hys Astensyon to heuen wyth oure kyndeffor thyn holy
                    Assumptoun on vs haue þow mynde
Bod549.Attributed Title: The V Ioyes to oure Lady (f. 78v)
